  "detailed_description": "<h1>CHECK OUT OUR GAME</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Bike, nature and you</h2>Rde along beautiful forest landscapes, rivers and mountains. Enjoy birdsong, explore dense forests and make your own route! Accelerate, jump, explore and try not to crash on your way!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903400/extras/3f81afdb8c0c5cc49d095382de269343.poster.avif?t=1659718232\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903400/extras/3f81afdb8c0c5cc49d095382de269343.webm?t=1659718232\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903400/extras/3f81afdb8c0c5cc49d095382de269343.mp4?t=1659718232\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Journey waiting for you!</h2>Explore nature at your own pace or challenge other players to compete for the best trail time. Follow the route or create your own, but be careful and try to crash as little as possible.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903400/extras/e1188d3c130562053d2b0d3bfb15bda3.poster.avif?t=1659718232\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903400/extras/e1188d3c130562053d2b0d3bfb15bda3.webm?t=1659718232\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903400/extras/e1188d3c130562053d2b0d3bfb15bda3.mp4?t=1659718232\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Full immersion</h2>What could be better than nature and a bike? - Ride for fun, forget about your problems and just enjoy it. Alternate between third-person view and first-person view, it will help you to experience the atmosphere better.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903400/extras/5fcd3bf918129ca643d851b4063338eb.poster.avif?t=1659718232\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903400/extras/5fcd3bf918129ca643d851b4063338eb.webm?t=1659718232\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903400/extras/5fcd3bf918129ca643d851b4063338eb.mp4?t=1659718232\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Relax and drive</h2>Don't like high speed? - Then choose a comfortable pace and just enjoy the views, explore the track carefully and you can unlock all the characters, collect coins and buy new bikes, clothes.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Have a nice trip!</h2>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Bike, nature and you</h2>Rde along beautiful forest landscapes, rivers and mountains. Enjoy birdsong, explore dense forests and make your own route! Accelerate, jump, explore and try not to crash on your way!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903400/extras/3f81afdb8c0c5cc49d095382de269343.poster.avif?t=1659718232\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903400/extras/3f81afdb8c0c5cc49d095382de269343.webm?t=1659718232\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903400/extras/3f81afdb8c0c5cc49d095382de269343.mp4?t=1659718232\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Journey waiting for you!</h2>Explore nature at your own pace or challenge other players to compete for the best trail time. Follow the route or create your own, but be careful and try to crash as little as possible.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903400/extras/e1188d3c130562053d2b0d3bfb15bda3.poster.avif?t=1659718232\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903400/extras/e1188d3c130562053d2b0d3bfb15bda3.webm?t=1659718232\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903400/extras/e1188d3c130562053d2b0d3bfb15bda3.mp4?t=1659718232\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Full immersion</h2>What could be better than nature and a bike? - Ride for fun, forget about your problems and just enjoy it. Alternate between third-person view and first-person view, it will help you to experience the atmosphere better.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903400/extras/5fcd3bf918129ca643d851b4063338eb.poster.avif?t=1659718232\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903400/extras/5fcd3bf918129ca643d851b4063338eb.webm?t=1659718232\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1903400/extras/5fcd3bf918129ca643d851b4063338eb.mp4?t=1659718232\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Relax and drive</h2>Don't like high speed? - Then choose a comfortable pace and just enjoy the views, explore the track carefully and you can unlock all the characters, collect coins and buy new bikes, clothes.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Have a nice trip!</h2>",
